<item>
            <title>[LU-13153] Function llapi_get_version_string fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13153</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The llapi function &lt;tt&gt;llapi_get_version_string&lt;/tt&gt; always (AFAICT) fails with ENOENT because it passes the argument to &lt;tt&gt;get_lustre_param_value&lt;/tt&gt; in the wrong order.&lt;br/&gt;
 I should add that this function is used in &lt;tt&gt;jt_get_version&lt;/tt&gt; that has a fallback to &lt;tt&gt;LUSTRE_VERSION_STRING&lt;/tt&gt; which might have shadowed the error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a simple patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
